               Whipped
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17870110-19-punish106" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870110-19-punish106" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870110-19-defend208 t17870110-19-punish106"></join>
               imprisoned three months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice WILSON.</p>
